horizpa.horizpar: Origin of data is from survey monuments and documentation. There are areas in the eastern part of the City and the Charles River where there are no known monuments. This is due to some areas being historical tidelands and the boundary at one time was the center of a now filled waterway. Efforts are being made to correct these areas through survey and research of historical maps and documents. (MGL Chapter 42, Sec. 12).
